    {
      "texte": "National Communism or 'NazComm' is a communism practiced at a national level. National communism recognises that both globalist capitalism",
      "texte_balise": "National Communism or 'NazComm' is a communism practiced at a national level. National communism recognises that both globalist capitalism",
      "bbox": [
        52.0,
        694.0,
        994.0,
        706.0
      ],
      "confiance": 1.0
    },
    {
      "texte": "and international communism aim to destroy traditional proletariat culture. We find our basis in the writings of Marx, Engels, Lenin, Stalin, Kim",
      "texte_balise": "and international communism aim to destroy traditional proletariat culture. We find our basis in the writings of Marx, Engels, Lenin, Stalin, Kim",
      "bbox": [
        58.0,
        710.0,
        986.0,
        726.0
      ],
      "confiance": 1.0
    },
    {
      "texte": "Il-Sung, etc. We recognise that a communist revolution will inevitably begin at a national level as a struggle between proletariat and bourgeoisie",
      "texte_balise": "Il-Sung, etc. We recognise that a communist revolution will inevitably begin at a national level as a struggle between proletariat and bourgeoisie",
      "bbox": [
        52.0,
        728.0,
        990.0,
        742.0
      ],
      "confiance": 1.0
    },
    {
      "texte": "made inevitable by the modern conditions of capitalism. National communism recognises that the international bourgeoisie will attempt to destroy",
      "texte_balise": "made inevitable by the modern conditions of capitalism. National communism recognises that the international bourgeoisie will attempt to destroy",
      "bbox": [
        46.0,
        744.0,
        998.0,
        758.0
      ],
      "confiance": 1.0
    },
    {
      "texte": "all attempts at escape from capitalism, therefore, we stress the need for self-sustaining national communes, capable of resisting globalist capital-",
      "texte_balise": "all attempts at escape from capitalism, therefore, we stress the need for self-sustaining national communes, capable of resisting globalist capital-",
